@page "/membership"

<PageTitle>Gotorz Membership</PageTitle>

<div class="container my-5 text-center">
    <!-- Section Headline -->
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #f8b500;">Gotorz</h2>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4">Gotorz Membership</h4>

    <!-- White Content Box -->
    <div class="mx-auto p-4 text-start"
         style="
             background-color: white;
             border-radius: 5px;
             border: 1px solid lightgrey;
             box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
             max-width: 1000px;
             line-height: 1.8;
         ">
        <p>
            Our loyal clients who have booked with Gotorz more than once are eligible for membership!
            If none of our agents have reached out to you to activate it, please contact our customer care team to gain access.
            Gotorz membership unlocks exclusive member-only benefits including travel flexibility, refund prioritization, and access to personalized promotions —
            in addition to discounts only available through your membership tier.
        </p>

        <p>Here’s a breakdown of the current membership types and their benefits:</p>

        <!-- Gold Membership -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">🌟 Gold Membership:</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>15% discount on selected offers on the site.</li>
            <li>Flexible refund policy: 75% to 100% refund on eligible bookings.</li>
            <li>Referral reward: €15 discount for every new customer referred by the member.</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Silver Membership -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">🥈 Silver Membership:</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>10% discount on selected offers on the site.</li>
            <li>Flexible refund policy: 40% to 70% refund on eligible bookings.</li>
            <li>Referral reward: €15 discount for every new customer referred by the member.</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Bronze Membership -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">🥉 Bronze Membership:</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>5% discount on selected offers on the site.</li>
            <li>Flexible refund policy: 20% to 40% refund on eligible bookings.</li>
            <li>Referral reward: €15 discount for every new customer referred by the member.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-4">
            <strong>Note:</strong> Gotorz reserves the right to limit membership benefits to one use per reservation.
            For more details about your tier, please reach out to our support team.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
